# HabitForge — Master Root Gitignore
# Senior-grade exclusion patterns for MERN + Python Monorepo

# [Node.js — Backend & Frontend]
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
**/.DS_Store
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.eslintcache

# [Python — ML Service]
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*$py.class
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/env/
**/ENV/

# [Machine Learning Artifacts — Keep code, exclude large trained binaries if necessary]
# Note: Keeping small model artifacts is fine, but exclude huge checkpoints
**/checkpoints/

# [System / IDE]
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
.antigravityignore/
